The paper presents algorithms for learning recursive logic programs, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the computational complexity of the learning problem, which could place it under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
